ependent'' of $t$, i.e.\\\ninvariant by parallel transport under the $(1,1)$-component of the Gauss-Manin\nconnection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 May 2001 08:55:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Sep 2001 13:51:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
